  "description": "Me and my family have been living near the small community of Porcupine, on the Pine Ridge Indian Reservation, for about a month now. We were invited because of our experience with regenerative horticulture and sustainable resource management oriented toward ending food apartheid, and so we\u0026rsquo;ve been taking time talking with folk to see how those skills should be applied here. And, we think we know what we should do:\n",
